edu.umass.cs.msocket

Class FlowIDToControllerMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.msocket.FlowIDToControllerMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class FlowIDToControllerMapping
extends Object
implements Runnable
    This class implements a UDP controller for an interface on the client side. On the client side, there can be one UDP controller per interface. The class also keeps a mapping of all the MSocket clients that use this UDP controller.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Emmanuel Cecchet
